summary: An Ordinance providing for the payment of the cost and expense of the laying off, extending, widening, and establishing of Twenty-eighth Avenue Northeast, from East Fifty-fifth Street to a point three hundred eighty-two and fifth one-hundredths (382.50) feet north therefrom, as provided for in Ordinance No. 33023 of the City of Seattle, by the issuance and sale of bonds of the district created to pay therefor.
